{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>現場所見，事主站在單位窗外，整個人穿在晾衫架的欄杆之間，掛出一橫幅寫上「黑箱作業」、「迫害老人」等字句，暫未清楚事主的訴求。直到下午2時許，消防員終將男子帶返屋內。</p><p>現場消息指，事主任職地盤水泥工人，近日疑被欠薪，加上有家庭問題，所以在窗外危坐控訴。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123604610800422912780536.jpeg/dFEufDwkCzZKSwzE805RPIMIW_4bxqHlJBvDoyQbw6M\" alt=\"男子拿出白底紅字橫幅控訴，企圖尋短。\"><figcaption>男子拿出白底紅字橫幅控訴，企圖尋短。</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123609682108223488928043.jpeg/p_bO7s2qPYOUo9m9bXAA4ZwiaBzi6hBQbOSsJUbkrCU\" alt=\"談判專家遞給男子一份文件。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>談判專家遞給男子一份文件。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123604303983153152893517.jpeg/tJbJYoOkt8-GxkYbc2Yz9vu4lUG2BFnJLm6SxC5uksQ\" alt=\"男子爬出窗外，手持「血書」控訴。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>男子爬出窗外，手持「血書」控訴。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123604296596721664713846.jpeg/lIv1lfNXqQdEjVMtUGBOAbJMtL3cpuMlWqQdn1qkHZ8\" alt=\"現場為將軍澳厚德邨德安樓一高層單位。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>現場為將軍澳厚德邨德安樓一高層單位。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123610034886938624306745.jpeg/uzxJzBHynxYFTUtK2pqJpW6u03OcLZM9KqTciwCk3Is\" alt=\"現場為將軍澳厚德邨德安樓。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>現場為將軍澳厚德邨德安樓。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123610038288650240427609.jpeg/DE2U3VvePZpBlE6rvE3tW3JoW7qGhof32ov_c_CL_3M\" alt=\"消防接報到場。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>消防接報到場。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123610042172706816267145.jpeg/GlyxhZydn202W65BEbI600IxKopb9Ar1J1t1Mw1bdTM\" alt=\"消防打開氣墊救援。（黃學潤攝）\"><figcaption>消防打開氣墊救援。（黃學潤攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123597233099378688610379.jpeg/xcyS4hbp9lISFrJvkTExh2IqVYtzV_2iaZd_FmmXfxY\" alt=\"消防車到場戒備。（讀者提供）\"><figcaption>消防車到場戒備。（讀者提供）</figcaption></figure><p>求助網站和熱線：</p><p>即睇3分鐘情緒自救法　呼吸間即可